<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-container>
      <v-row justify="center">
        <v-col cols="12" sm="8" md="4">
          <v-card>
            <v-card-title class="headline">Qui êtes vous ? </v-card-title>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-form>
                <v-text-field label="Prénom" v-model="firstname"></v-text-field>
                <v-text-field label="Nom" v-model="lastname"></v-text-field>
              </v-form>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-card-actions>
              <v-spacer></v-spacer>
              <router-link to="/list"><v-btn color="primary" @click="login">Connexion</v-btn></router-link>
            </v-card-actions>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
data() {
return {
firstname: '',
lastname: '',
}
},
methods: {
login() {
this.$router.push({name:'ListPage', params: {firstname: this.firstname, lastname: this.lastname}})
}
}
}
</script>
